{
  "stem": "22174.7",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1955.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But before that, [INAUDIBLE], after the end of the war, I got married.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I told my wife that I want [INAUDIBLE], and I wanted to leave Palestine.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So she said, OK, if you want to leave.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She-- she did not think of leaving because she was really-- she was-- she was more realistic than I.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She had a very hard time also there, very hard time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But she was more, more practical than-- than I was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was kind of naive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, when I came, I was naive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I was-- I was disillusioned easily.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But my wife came-- came from a very poor family.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she actually left Austria to get away from the poverty and came-- and went to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then she went into-- she was sent into an agricultural school for women.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And also, there a hard time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And-- but she was tough.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was really-- And-- and then, she-- she founded, with some other-- some other eight-- eight people I think, she founded a new kibbutz, a new settlement in the Jordan Valley.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then when the war broke out, her parents were left in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And she-- so she wanted to-- to get her parents out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And her-- her sister said-- one of her sisters said, we have to leave the kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Because we have to try and make money for our parents to come, to get them here.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So she left the kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Then-- but-- and then she-- one day, she stood in Tel Aviv from, I don't know, 4 o'clock in the morning or all day long, I think, at the consulate, [INAUDIBLE] consulate, to ask to-- to get a visa, an entrance visa.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And she couldn't get one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So she didn't-- they get her parents out either.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
